{"tid":884844,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我曾經以為自己諗通左，但原來我每日都有輕生的念頭","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T03:16:55.000Z","uid":82593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c29545d3749dc16275b49603e005b73adc8e82a","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"求生存之道"},{"pid":"ce13a29e4fc047aea39b990d77f5cb6ba0be472a","tid":884844,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"咩事令你想輕生？"},{"pid":"dfd6601eb9ec21075304165d84602fc6f7987202","tid":884844,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"重生"},{"pid":"cd76efed8c953a5f1c4303c5c8b3ba4fc9b87d7a","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce13a29e4fc047aea39b990d77f5cb6ba0be472a","tid":884844,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"咩事令你想輕生？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"對勝負，對正確，對成功非常執著。<br />\n<br />\n每每做錯一個決定，或是在挑戰/事業/經濟上的挫敗，都會好辛苦，好執著。"},{"pid":"56badfc2fc2500f37ecae939dbbe675e4604a8cd","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"起源小時候，好多野都要靠自己爭取，靠成績先可以獲得，所以有好強的勝負慾，仍對自己有好高的要求，奈何冇咩天份。"},{"pid":"90d3743006d3fb81c8ded75da83e5827b5ed2f54","tid":884844,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"殉情吧"},{"pid":"378c0a94a194b643d512c446c937c19f0023e7c5","tid":884844,"uid":205709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd76efed8c953a5f1c4303c5c8b3ba4fc9b87d7a","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce13a29e4fc047aea39b990d77f5cb6ba0be472a","tid":884844,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"咩事令你想輕生？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"對勝負，對正確，對成功非常執著。<br />\n<br />\n每每做錯一個決定，或是在挑戰/事業/經濟上的挫敗，都會好辛苦，好執著。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f358345a1f8eb61587e39d10373a7cb9de05db8","tid":884844,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"一樣"},{"pid":"d129143e34b45ada1ee97d1b9157659f9f4a1024","tid":884844,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"才是唇膏境界~~~<img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.com/albums/ah233/sorsawsor/Smoke_zpswiq0jsie.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1381.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2FSmoke_zpswiq0jsie.gif&h=5f54e144&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.com/albums/ah233/sorsawsor/nRdNt_zpsg8vhkurp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1381.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2FnRdNt_zpsg8vhkurp.gif&h=e11d9c2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2913943832abeb0ac05d62e65afb2bff7288a265","tid":884844,"uid":36402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd76efed8c953a5f1c4303c5c8b3ba4fc9b87d7a","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce13a29e4fc047aea39b990d77f5cb6ba0be472a","tid":884844,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"咩事令你想輕生？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"對勝負，對正確，對成功非常執著。<br />\n<br />\n每每做錯一個決定，或是在挑戰/事業/經濟上的挫敗，都會好辛苦，好執著。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"既然係自己執著，就要靠自己睇化睇淡<br />\n勝負，正確，成功都無絕對既一面<br />\n我覺得挫敗係好正常，因為我哋係普通人，每個人都會做錯，原諒下自己，睇開啲自己既執著，你都可以贏，正確同成功。"},{"pid":"eed27efa4fcaddf6651672f3eb95a13787e1dc56","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"我每一日都同自己講:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;算啦，決定都過去左，唔好咁執著。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但都冇用，每一日都仍有輕生的念頭。"},{"pid":"7df5d26839421d8b9ef1b2a210b5ad5a889c40b8","tid":884844,"uid":105660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"同路人<br />\n<br />\n之前depress 到胃 腸出血 野都食唔到咁<br />\n<br />\n之後同自己講 只要胃腸好返  我就會開開心心咁過日子 <br />\n<br />\n好翻之後 的確強迫住自己唔好同人比較 唔好唔開心 但總會有一段時間 想輕生 depress既心境 就好似跟一世咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c8b077e8f25c577f5f139af4b5d6355cfd6ebf","tid":884844,"uid":140092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"以前都好計較勝負，對方都係咁。但近排學識凡事笑住噉享受個競爭，輸都當係個學習過程。咁做，反而會亂埋對方競爭者嘅陣腳，因為佢想你爭，但你好似唔係想爭。"},{"pid":"bcbfa7d7ac48b76b5b1ce21b46be870606e8bf24","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7df5d26839421d8b9ef1b2a210b5ad5a889c40b8","tid":884844,"uid":105660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"同路人<br />\n<br />\n之前depress 到胃 腸出血 野都食唔到咁<br />\n<br />\n之後同自己講 只要胃腸好返  我就會開開心心咁過日子 <br />\n<br />\n好翻之後 的確強迫住自己唔好同人比較 唔好唔開心 但總會有一段時間 想輕生 depress既心境 就好似跟一世咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"冇錯，個種DEPRESS的反應就好似本能咁。<br />\n<br />\n其實我都試過鼓勵自己，試過用父母的相做電話WALLPAPER去提醒自己仲有個家，但仍然徒勞無功。<br />\n<br />\n我只係好怕，有一日會有一刻的衝動，去完成呢件事..."},{"pid":"78e7f71488b6d10312b9056547f176bde79f85d8","tid":884844,"uid":200532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"boku ga shinou to omotta no wa<br />\n<br />\n聽吓歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d341f1a5c24151b955380193e72f899311b73a71","tid":884844,"uid":140092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"論成功，比失敗難好多倍，公司揼份proposal錯一隻字可以累街坊，計少咗個零可以成筆錢唔同。<br />\n<br />\n小弟做生意都係成日瀨嘢，俾錯價、交唔到貨、有啲嘢符合唔到預期。但諗係大把人做嘢錯多過你，就會覺得自己唔應該再諗自己有幾慘。"},{"pid":"111d81e1479f17f4c2edc9a680b6e10f08e1ec04","tid":884844,"uid":16986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"何必要做奴隸 無須要為失去了的執迷<br />\n能流淚畫臉像四季 做人做過世 慢長年月有路軌<br />\n人總想擁有東西 要是代價高 越令心中牽繫<br />\n擔擾要是無謂 拿花灑洗禮"},{"pid":"33195845749f11d351b115f67b96b0de80ecb23b","tid":884844,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"樣衰想輕生"},{"pid":"394d1a0e5d6202f97e71d549c0824fb9d59def8c","tid":884844,"uid":82593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"我好少會比較，更多情況係將所有野攬哂上身。<br />\n<br />\n就算輸俾人，唔會怨人地叻，永遠只係怨自己廢物和自己唔夠料。"}]}